{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/StudentLogin/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<!-- Do Pandas eat bananas? Check out this short video that shows that yes! pandas do seem to really enjoy bananas!\n\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/4SZl1r2O_bY\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe> -->\n<h2 id=\"logging-in\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#logging-in\" aria-label=\"logging in permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Logging in</h2>\n<p><strong>Purpose:</strong> To access the Luminate system fully, a login form is\nprompted depending on the selected method of log in, i.e. Student Login,\nSchool Login and Content Creator Login.</p>\n<h3 id=\"student-account-creation\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#student-account-creation\" aria-label=\"student account creation permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Student Account Creation</h3>\n<p>Students without an account can access the system from the homepage by\nclicking <strong>‘Login’</strong> button on the side navigation bar, if student has\nan account already they can login, <a href=\"https://www.luminate.ng/LoginView\">via this link</a>.</p>\n<h4 id=\"how-to-login-student-as-an-existing-user\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#how-to-login-student-as-an-existing-user\" aria-label=\"how to login student as an existing user permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to login Student as an existing User</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Enter your Email address</li>\n<li>Enter your Password</li>\n<li>Click on the login button to direct you to the student dashboard</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"how-to-logout-student-from-the-system\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#how-to-logout-student-from-the-system\" aria-label=\"how to logout student from the system permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to logout Student from the System</h4>\n<p> To exit an existing User from the system:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Click on the signed in user icon at the top right corner of the page,\nthen</li>\n<li>Click on the <strong>“Log Out”</strong> button to exit User from the system</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"how-to-create-student-account-for-the-first-time\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#how-to-create-student-account-for-the-first-time\" aria-label=\"how to create student account for the first time permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to Create Student Account for the first time</h4>\n<p> To exit an existing User from the system:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Click on <strong>Sign up</strong></li>\n<li>Select User's learning path</li>\n<li>Click on <strong>Next</strong> button</li>\n<li>Enter Email address</li>\n<li>Click on verify button</li>\n<li>An email has been sent to your mail to activate account</li>\n<li>Click on the , activate  button, to activate account</li>\n<li>Enter User First Name and Last Name</li>\n<li>Enter new password, retype new password</li>\n<li>Click on Agree to terms and conditions</li>\n<li>Click on <b>Sign Up</b> button to direct User to student dashboard</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Student Login"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/StudentLogin/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}